{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "圣城被僵尸包围。然而阿加莎查明了\\n它们的来历以及操纵它们的魔导书。\\n与此同时，梅露莎发现僵尸\\n会因穿着变装的自己而陷入混乱，\\n由此想到了打开局面的办法。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "僵尸来袭几小时后……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "虽然有不少僵尸\\n都追着王子殿下他们\\n往森林那边去了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "但还是有一部分僵尸\\n在外面游荡啊。\\n还好它们没有进到里面来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村落的少女",
            "context": "唔，大姐姐。\\n我们不会被僵尸吃掉吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "放心吧。这座城很坚固，\\n门窗也都关好了，\\n它们进不来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "况且在王子殿下他们回来前，\\n我们会保护大家的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "（没错……在此之前\\n就只能靠我们了！）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "陷入狂乱的祭司",
            "context": "没用的！蔓延的邪恶亡灵\\n会吞食我们所有人。\\n我们注定要成为它们的盘中餐！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "陷入狂乱的祭司",
            "context": "地狱无法容纳的亡者现于人世，\\n28天后我们将迎来死亡的黎明！\\n整片大陆都会化作亡者之地！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "那、那个，请冷静一点！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120171_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗卡族师父",
            "context": "没法冷静……冷静不下来！\\n要是手上有活儿\\n倒是能分散一下注意力！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120173_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗卡族徒弟",
            "context": "师父！我就知道你会这么说，\\n所以找来了能用来打铁的铁管！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "那是爱德华的私人物品！\\n怎么能擅自拿来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "刚才的爆炸，是怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120095_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蓬莱工匠",
            "context": "抱歉。看到稀有的仙花焰，\\n我忍不住就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "请别乱动，很危险的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "恐惧和焦躁\\n让大家陷入了恐慌……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "一对情侣中的男方",
            "context": "这次又怎么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "一对情侣中的女方",
            "context": "也许是僵尸们\\n受到巨大动静的影响……\\n开始敲打墙壁了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村落的少女",
            "context": "呜哇！好可怕啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "没事，一定会没事的。\\n它们马上就会厌倦\\n然后散去的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "好像真的厌倦了呢……呼。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "但是再这样下去，\\n心脏怕是承受不住……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "哼！就因为没有可靠的领袖，\\n大家才会担惊受怕。\\n所以，就由我来领导大家！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（莫西干头）",
            "context": "哇哦！不愧是大哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "那边那个软弱的森隐族女人。\\n这是领袖的第一道命令，\\n把这座城里所有食物都交出来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "这可不行。\\n食物是属于大家的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（莫西干头）",
            "context": "我大哥肚子饿了！敢反抗的话，\\n就让你吃不了兜着走！哇哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不管怎么说都不能\\n把食物全部交给你们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "嚯，小姑娘脾气不小嘛。\\n这下真得给你点颜色看看了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "哎呀，先生你不能这样。\\n暴力统治可没有好下场哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "啥？你也要反抗本大爷吗？\\n啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "请别碰这座城里的\\n任何食物……好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混们",
            "context": "是，我知道了，阿加莎大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "什么！？我们为什么\\n会回应那个女人！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "阿加莎，谢谢你帮忙解围。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "之前都没看到你，\\n你跑哪去了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我去调查了一些东西，\\n因此明白了不少事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "首先是这些僵尸的身份。\\n准确说来它们并不是\\n现在的帝国兵，而是300年前的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "300年前！？\\n是那么久之前的人吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "说起来300年前\\n也有狄涅尔帝国呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我记得是在300年前的\\n第二次封魔战争中\\n被阿尔贝琉斯王毁灭了吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "莫非是那时的帝国兵\\n回来报仇了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "不，应该是魔导书的持有者\\n让它们来袭击这里的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "魔导书？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "《不死军之书》——\\n这是一本令亡者复活\\n并操纵它们的神秘禁书。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120018_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "一对情侣中的女方",
            "context": "没错！有个男人在湖边照着书念了\\n咒语之后，僵尸们就从地面涌出来了！\\n接着他就对僵尸们发号施令……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "我猜那片湖就是300年前的战场。\\n施法者应该就是在那里操纵僵尸们，\\n让它们对圣城发起进攻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "操纵僵尸的魔导书……\\n那要是能把魔导书从那个人手上\\n抢过来，也许就能阻止僵尸了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "这主意不错。\\n但前提是我们能前往\\n施法者所在的那片湖。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "唔……确实很困难啊。\\n毕竟外面还有僵尸在晃悠……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村落的少女",
            "context": "大姐姐，不好了！\\n光头大叔和莫西干头大叔\\n从窗户跑到外面去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶！？不会吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "村落的少女",
            "context": "他们说既然吃不到城里的食物，\\n那就去吃外面的点心之家。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "本来是为了让他们\\n别擅自行动才施加的“魅惑”，\\n好像适得其反了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "这、这下不妙啊！\\n得赶快把他们带回来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "趁现在没有僵尸！\\n点心之家吃到饱！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（莫西干头）",
            "context": "咬咬咬……呀哈！\\n这棉花糖真甜啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "干嘛？我正忙着\\n吃巧克力墙呢，等下再说。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "我——说——了——\\n等下再说……\\n呃、哇啊啊啊啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（莫西干头）",
            "context": "什、什么时候被包围了！？\\n看招！看招看招！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "没、没用！再这样下去\\n我们会变成僵尸的点心！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混们",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120202_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "你们没事吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "什么！？你怎么会在这里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "我来救你们了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120202_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "僵尸",
            "context": "啊啊？唔啊啊啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（莫西干头）",
            "context": "咦？僵尸们没有冲过来袭击我们。\\n好像是看到小姑娘之后\\n就陷入了混乱……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "（它们面对其他人\\n都毫不犹豫地发动攻击，\\n为什么唯独面对我……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "（看见我……我的装束……\\n难道说……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "漂亮，命中头部！\\n梅露莎，你没事吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "嗯！快，趁现在\\n躲进屋子里吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120033_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "小混混（光头）",
            "context": "哎哟喂，得救了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "那是什么态度啊？\\n看上去一点都没有反省。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110341_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿加莎",
            "context": "像那种威胁他人\\n还不知感恩的人，\\n放着不管不就行了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "不管对方是怎样的人，\\n都不能见死不救。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "先不说这个，希里丝，阿加莎。\\n我想到了一个办法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22205_02_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}